# Nice collection of body typefaces

There is a growing list of great looking typefaces on [Google's
directory](http://www.google.com/webfonts), however most look better for
headlines. [Ross
Johnson](https://twitter.com/#!/3pointross) has put together [a
list of great typefaces for body
copy](http://3.7designs.co/blog/web-fonts-for-body-copy/), explaining
his selection criteria in [his blog
post](http://3.7designs.co/blog/2012/01/40-web-fonts-for-body-copy/).

Unless you're reading this in your newsreader, you're enjoying
[Bitter](http://www.google.com/webfonts/specimen/Bitter).
